OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe best of the sunshine will
OL,6,Fbe across the southeast, where it will
OL,7,Ffeel increasingly hot and humid.
OL,8,FElsewhere, it will be rather cloudy,
OL,9,Fwith a little showery rain possible at
OL,10,Ftimes, particularly across parts of
OL,11,FScotland and northern England.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA widely warm night with
OL,14,Fmostly light winds. There is still a
OL,15,Fchance of showers across some central
OL,16,Fareas, but most places will stay dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
