OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAny showers will soon clear
OL,6,Finto the North Sea, leaving all parts
OL,7,Fof the country widely fine, settled
OL,8,Fand hot. It will feel particularly hot
OL,9,Fand humid across the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
